{"tid":1741130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渠道暢通，有你幫手，必定會成功","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:54.000Z","uid":217430,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6933a7f98c6d7f46ab363b122926d9e8b19573","tid":1741130,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9y1CQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9y1CQa.jpg&h=fdaff18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日經過金馬倫。成條路既渠口面都疊滿曬建築廢料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5llKrmPPzug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5llKrmPPzug&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=ad4f1a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5llKrmPPzug</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏天，為大地帶來雨水⋯⋯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你。秋天唔撚會落雨呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n疏導雨水，需要暢通的渠道<br />\n但當遇到隨處拋棄的垃圾、建築廢料和油污<br />\n淤塞的渠道就會為我們帶來煩惱<br />\n渠道暢通，有你幫手，必定會成功<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">渠務投訴熱線 2300 1110</span></span>"},{"pid":"54c081ae2ce7af6ffe9e3ad72f685c8cec1c359f","tid":1741130,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"用1823都得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5ab631f795c3757814fc6dd7fb9cff6a70cb4b","tid":1741130,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"良好市民自推1/5"},{"pid":"f371e7ae9e514a56b40586c7a0c6eb9b51a901e6","tid":1741130,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"良好市民自推2/5"},{"pid":"4416c2e7acca94522f7683498e102061d94160ae","tid":1741130,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"